title: Jojoin Inflatable Volleyball Set, 115” Inflatable Pool Float Set Include Basketball Hoop Set & Balls Floating Swimming Pool Toy Pool Volleyball Game for Kids and Adults (115” x 38” x 28”)
description: Product Description POOL INFLATABLE VOLLEYBALL SET Fun pool volleyball game, includes an inflatable volleyball court with 2 weight bags, an inflatable volleyball ball, an basketball hoop set, and a storage bag, perfect summer swimming pool games for party, activity, ceremony, carnival, birthday parties or summer gift. Summer fun swimming pool games toys for boys girls ... Large Size The dimensions of the inflatable volleyball court are 115" x 38" x 28", designed larger size for more people to play together, ideal for giant-size fun in the swimming pool! Safe & Durable Material Our floating volleyball set is made of environmently PVC material, durable, scratch-resistant, no smell, safe for kids to play, the best swimming pool game toy for summer. With Storage Bag Delivered with a drawstring storage bag for you to store your volleyball set when you don't want to play it, conveniently save it in the cabinet, storage room or any other place. Add Weight to Keep in Place The inflatable volleyball court comes with 2 weight bags to add anchor weights, prevent the volleyball rack from floating during play. Attach the weight bag at the end of the both side, add some weight things into it, and then put it in the water. Inflatable Pool Float Can be used as summer pool float, just take the net off, and kids or adults can lie on the volleyball court to feel the cool in the hot summer. Fun Garden Volleyball You can also play the inflatable volleyball set on the land or beach, have fun with your kids, enjoy the parent-child time. Not only can be played in summer, you can play it all year round. More Product Detail: Material: 0.28 mm PVC, the net is made of polypropylene Size: volleyball rack: 115 x 38 x 28 inch Basketball Hoop: 23 x 23 x 21 inch Volleyball: 20 inch Basketball: 11 inch Weight Bag: 12 x 10 inch Storage Bag: 26 x 17 inch Package Include: 1 x Volleyball Rack 1 x Volleyball 1 x Basketball 1 x Basketball Hoop 1 x Storage Bag 2 x Weight Bags How to install the volleyball net? 1. Open the net, you can see that there are holes for installing the net on both sides of the net, and there are also a row of holes for installing the net on the edge of the volleyball rack; 2. Tie a string through the hole on the edge of the net, and then pass the string through the hole on the volleyball rack and tie it to the top; 3. Pass the rope down through the second hole of the net, and then tie the rope over the hole of the volleyball rack; 4. Then go through the bottom hole of the net and tie the rope to the volleyball rack; 5. Do the same operation to the other side of the net as above; 6. Finish.
